{"tid":2220594,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"追女，個心囉囉攣","createTime":"2020-09-27T18:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T11:19:13.000Z","uid":373421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6b58e596e810117c70745ec1287c102e9bb548d6","tid":2220594,"uid":373421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T18:55:34.000Z","msg":"識左個女仔，見過幾次了，平時都會係通訊軟件吹水，大家都幾夾，起碼我覺得先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都讚過我可愛，又話我成日笑好nice<br />\n見過面幾次，今日都約到出黎，有講有笑，甚至有肢體接觸，係佢掂我，（ 我先唔會隨便掂女仔咁cheap<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）食埋晚飯，最後去到党鐵站就分開左<br />\n因為我暫時仲係感覺唔到佢釋出嘅訊號<br />\n有時好冷漠，有時又會熱情如火<br />\n想去馬，但驚失敗，朋友都沒得做<br />\n起碼友誼永固<br />\n但又唔想失去呢個機會<br />\n嚟緊中秋節同聖誕節都會再進一步行動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都幾鐘意佢架，唔係話好靚，但性格完全係我心目中想要嘅伴侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e4630fa81dca850fe0589d1f0f8f245e1982e1","tid":2220594,"uid":27251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T18:57:39.000Z","msg":"通常都係你對人有意思，先會咁敏感，人地當你新朋友，你表白就領野，除非你好靚仔，條女就一早表態啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7194135a0e72228b77d427eec9d6afe717e16a1c","tid":2220594,"uid":244313,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T19:02:05.000Z","msg":"我完全同巴打你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢好慢熱 <br />\n仲要好被動嗰隻 而我都係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔識做主動<br />\n諗住同佢傾多幾個月 傾到深入啲先去馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n共勉之"},{"pid":"79ec4a9702701315f92d22f7569c12f7910cbc41","tid":2220594,"uid":373421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d2e4630fa81dca850fe0589d1f0f8f245e1982e1","tid":2220594,"uid":27